{"tid":536350,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"牙科-洗完牙隻牙痛到爆","createTime":"2018-01-21T16:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T08:30:08.000Z","uid":23676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1e77eee09490d50beacbb6134dc0528971982030","tid":536350,"uid":23676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:42:50.000Z","msg":"有無牙醫或者姑娘知點解洗完牙都兩日，隻牙仲係痛到爆。洗個陣呢一隻已經勁痛，係痛到喊個隻。<br />\n上網睇過話有機會隻牙裂左，真係咁誇張？有無人試過，同埋如果真係既話可以點處理，又可唔可以追討番個洗牙診所？"},{"pid":"1c7bc65015b24b544e4a9ec1eca42ddd54fae7cb","tid":536350,"uid":23676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:44:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9694ec692dd46612218c147b523897bc8a607889","tid":536350,"uid":23676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:47:13.000Z","msg":"推 求有心人解答一下"},{"pid":"9e49ec12a4fdc964f14f088df1db05a24a197d8c","tid":536350,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:52:24.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"907d2faebef485c1c4a646d6abc9b398870e88ec","tid":536350,"uid":3649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:53:06.000Z","msg":"你痛就要聽朝即刻搵牙醫架啦，<br />\n我話冇嘢你都唔信啦<br />\n<br />\n我就唔係洗牙，<br />\n不過食食吓嘢隻牙裂左開始痛，<br />\n原來係之前補牙嘅物料鬆左，<br />\n最後要杜牙根痛到仆街  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n快啲去睇牙醫啦巴打"},{"pid":"9f1da6e6670fcc4187ee982d590c3baf6afb1acb","tid":536350,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:53:42.000Z","msg":"打電話返去牙醫度話有問題"},{"pid":"b0851548cab971443ef73e4cf55a7ed8deb541db","tid":536350,"uid":23676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f1da6e6670fcc4187ee982d590c3baf6afb1acb","tid":536350,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T16:53:42.000Z","msg":"打電話返去牙醫度話有問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"有諗過 但最快都要聽日打"},{"pid":"4fab0a8429bffc5108fc39c2b53